ht-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(9) log level/ log file name/ cell group id/ llim timer/ csc/ timer/ uecc timer/ no of uecc/vendor info/ pdcp threshold / rat data volume/ gnb operating mode/ shm/ ue context list size/ network ip /&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;uecc mapping[8]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(10) no of uecc/ core no/ uecc mapping[8] / timer info/ uecc timer/ ue context list size/ ope mode/ total dc ue supported/ rat data volume&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(11) csc timer/ sfn offset/ max no support cell/ no of uecc/ num support ue per cell [32]/ health monitor&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(12) no uecc/ max num suppord ue per cell [32]/ timer info/ llim health monitor&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(13) log level / num amf/ amf comm info (ip, sctp stream/asso) / ngap local comm info / local port/ sctp conf param/ total ue supported / uecc num mapping / ran info (drx, ran node name/ ran node id)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(14)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(15)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;gnb operating mode/ son comm info/ x2ap info (log level, enb comm info, conf param, server cell [] , neighbor array [] (enb + gnb ) -&amp;gt; earfcn, pci ecgi,...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(16) num cell served/&amp;nbsp; cell index arr [32]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(17) ll/ gnb cu name/ num du/ du comm info/ local cu comm info/ sctp conf param/ timer info/ no of uecc/ uecc mapping[8]&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(18) num du/ du update info [ max du] -&amp;gt; num cell/ cell info [max cell per du]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(19) ll/ thread info/ pdcp timer&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(20) response code&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(21) -(23)&amp;nbsp; ll/ ipv4/ipv6/thread.///&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(22)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(25) gci/ ran info/ epc param/ ssb freq/ drx/ arfcn/ son enable&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(26) nr gci/ gci/ ran info/ ssb freq/ meas result/ block cell param ho/ l2 comm info (pdcp + egtpu)/ drx/ son enable/ arfcn/ immediate start&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(27) gci/ pdcp config [8]/ s1u config [8]/ nr system info (sib2- sib5)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(28) cell index/ pdcp config [32] / s1u config [32]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(29) pdcp